frames.caption: A surreal scene depicts a giant face with miniature figures working on it like artists and technicians. The figures are standing on scaffolding, using brushes and tools to enhance the features of the face. The image blends elements of art and fantasy, creating a whimsical atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene presents a creative and imaginative setting where tiny people are engaged in beautifying a large, realistic face. The figures appear to be artists or technicians meticulously working on the face, suggesting a theme of beauty enhancement or creation.

frames.caption: The image depicts a surreal scene where miniature figures are working on a woman's face as if it were a large-scale art project. The figures are using tools and scaffolding to apply makeup and enhance her features. The scene creatively combines elements of beauty and construction.
frames.description: This imaginative scene portrays a close-up of a woman's face being 'constructed' by tiny figures. The setting suggests a blend of beauty and artistry, with the figures meticulously applying makeup using brushes and scaffolding.
